About Me

Full-Stack AI Developer

I am a passionate full-stack developer with expertise in building web applications using modern technologies like React, Flask, and various AI/ML frameworks. My focus is on creating intuitive, efficient, and scalable applications that solve complex problems.

This demo showcases my ability to implement complex algorithms and present them through a user-friendly interface, combining theoretical computer science concepts with practical web development skills.

Technical Skills

Frontend
  • React, Redux, React Router
  • JavaScript/TypeScript
  • HTML5, CSS3, SASS
  • Bootstrap, Material-UI
Backend
  • Python (Flask, Django)
  • Node.js (Express)
  • RESTful API design
  • Database design (SQL, NoSQL)
AI/ML
  • Algorithm implementation
  • Data processing and visualization
  • Linear programming and optimization
  • Graph algorithms

Project Highlights

Santa Claus Algorithm Demo

This project demonstrates my ability to:

  • Implement complex algorithms from academic research
  • Create intuitive user interfaces for complex problems
  • Develop full-stack applications with React and Flask
  • Design responsive and user-friendly web applications
  • Handle data validation and error management
  • Provide clear visualization of algorithm results

The implementation follows the O(log log m / log log log m) approximation algorithm for the restricted assignment case of the Santa Claus Problem, as described in the paper by Bansal and Sviridenko.

Contact Information

I'm currently seeking opportunities where I can apply my skills in full-stack development and algorithm implementation. Feel free to reach out to me through the following channels:

  • Email: developer@example.com
  • LinkedIn: linkedin.com/in/fullstack-ai-developer
  • GitHub: github.com/fullstack-ai-dev

Note: Please replace with your actual contact information for job applications.
